 "body": "<p>Guidance on:</p>\n<ul><li class=\"filledcircle\">The commercial background and accountancy treatment of leasing is in the Business Leasing Manual at <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-leasing-manual/blm00001\" rel=\"nofollow\">BLM00001</a> onwards.</li><li class=\"filledcircle\">The taxation of leases is at <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-leasing-manual/blm30000\" rel=\"nofollow\">BLM30000</a>&nbsp;onwards, <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-leasing-manual/blm40000\">BLM40000</a> onwards and <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-leasing-manual/blm50000\">BLM50000</a> onwards.</li><li class=\"filledcircle\">Anti-avoidance legislation on leased trading assets and leased capital sums is at <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-income-manual/bim61200\">BIM61200</a> onwards.</li><li class=\"filledcircle\">Anti-avoidance legislation on sale and leaseback of land is at <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-income-manual/bim61300\">BIM61300</a> onwards.</li><li class=\"filledcircle\">Income from property is in the Property Income Manual (<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/property-income-manual/pim\">PIM</a>).</li></ul>\n",
